debrief.itemText: Please answer the following questions about your experience. Click and drag the red scrollbar to move down. Do not leave any box blank. Type ‘no’ or ‘n/a’ if you don’t have a response.
Briefly describe what you were asked to do in this experiment? (if there is existing text in the box delete it.
debrief.response: We were asked to very quickly answer between a number and a letter by approximately choosing each one an equal number of times without having a pattern of doing one then the other over and over again. We were asked to press the D key for  # below 153 and the F key for a # above 153. We were asked to press the J key for a letter closer to A and the K key for a letter closer to Z
